  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "It's been a while since I last saw you. How have you been? Unfortunate events have happened recently here in #m10004000#. A few days ago, a group of tribespeople went hunting in the swamp near #m10003000# to acquire some alligator skins, only to be ambushed by them. They came back alive, but they were seriously injured."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "People haven't gone to the swamp for quite some time, and during that time, the number of the alligators have dramatically increased to the point where they are starting to attack people. Even #p511# has taken notice, and he has been just as concerned about it as us. Can you help us, please?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you. Because of these recent events, #p511# decided to hire someone outside to take care of the alligators. Since he is a very busy man, however, I have assumed the task of picking out that someone to help us, and I choose you. So please head over to the swamp and take out #r100 #o29#s and 40 #o18#s#k and bring back #b20 #t4000018#s#k as evidence."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "The swamp can be reached through the sewage pipe in #m10003000#. I believe in you. Good luck."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You looked powerful enough to handle the task, at least in my eyes. Please reconsider your choice, because... if the alligators keep spawning like this in the swamp, it'll be really dangerous for everyone here down the road..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You're back early! That's incredible! I knew I had asked the right person for the job. Thanks to you, there should be considerably fewer alligators in the swamp now. Thank goodness..."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Did you bring the #b#t4000018#s#k with you? I also have something for you as a sign of my appreciation for your hard work. Which of these do you need?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "#b#t4000018#s#k can also be used as medicine. I wanted you to bring them so I could use them on people who have been attacked by the alligators. This scroll is our way of saying thanks, so please take it and put it to good use."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "sub"
        },
        "mob": {
          "_dirName": "mob",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "Please take out #r100 #o29#s and 40 #o18#s#k."
          }
        },
        "item": {
          "_dirName": "item",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "Please don’t forget to bring #b20 #t4000018#s#k."
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
